export const frd= 
`# **Quiz Application**\n\n---\n\n## **1. Application Overview**\n\nA web-based interactive quiz application that tests users' knowledge across multiple subjects with varying difficulty levels, real-time scoring, and session management.\n\n---\n\n## **2. User Roles**\n\n### **2.1 Quiz Taker (End User)**\n\n- Single role for all users  \n- All users have the same capabilities  \n- No authentication or user management required  \n- Session-based progress tracking  \n\n---\n\n## **3. Modules & Features**\n\n### **3.1 Quiz Setup Module**\n\n#### **3.1.1 Topic Selection**\n\n**Predefined Topics:**\n\n- Physics  \n- Biology  \n- Chemistry  \n- Mathematics  \n- Religion  \n\n**Custom Topic:**\n\n- \"Other\" option with text input  \n- Allows users to enter any custom subject  \n\n**Components:**\n\n- TopicDropdown  \n\n---\n\n#### **3.1.2 Difficulty Selection**\n\n**Levels:**\n\n- Simple (1 point per question)  \n- Intermediate (2 points per question)  \n- Advanced (3 points per question)  \n\n**Business Logic:**\n\n- Points awarded based on difficulty when answered correctly  \n\n---\n\n### **3.2 Quiz Session Module**\n\n#### **3.2.1 Question Management**\n\n**Limits & Types:**\n\n- 15 questions per session  \n- Multiple choice (A, B, C options)  \n- Single correct answer per question  \n\n**Question Sources:**\n\n- Local question bank for predefined topics  \n- LLM-generated questions for custom topics (placeholder)  \n\n**Tracking:**\n\n- Prevents duplicate questions in same session  \n- Tracks used question indices  \n- Resets pool when all questions exhausted  \n\n---\n\n#### **3.2.2 Timer System**\n\n**Duration:** 30 seconds per question  \n\n**Behavior:**\n\n- Countdown display  \n- Visual timer component  \n- Auto-submit when time expires  \n- Timer resets for each new question  \n\n**Components:**\n\n- Timer  \n\n---\n\n#### **3.2.3 Answer Submission**\n\n**Manual Submission:**\n\n- User selects answer and clicks submit  \n- Button disabled until answer selected  \n\n**Automatic Submission:**\n\n- Triggered on timeout  \n- Treated as incorrect answer  \n\n**Validation:**\n\n- Prevents multiple submissions  \n- Disables input after submission  \n\n---\n\n#### **3.2.4 New Question Feature**\n\n**Manual Skip:**\n\n- \"New Question\" button available during active question  \n- Increments question counter  \n- Fetches new question immediately  \n- Disabled after answer submission  \n\n---\n\n### **3.3 Scoring & Progress Module**\n\n#### **3.3.1 Score Tracking**\n\n**Real-time Updates:**\n\n- Points accumulated based on difficulty  \n- Correct answer count  \n- Total questions answered  \n- Accuracy percentage calculation  \n\n**Display Components:**\n\n- Current score (total points)  \n- Correct/Total ratio  \n- Accuracy percentage (decimal precision)  \n\n**Components:**\n\n- Scoreboard  \n\n---\n\n#### **3.3.2 Progress Indicators**\n\n- Question Counter: \"Q1/15\" format  \n- Topic Display: Current quiz topic  \n- Difficulty Badge: Visual indicator of difficulty level  \n- Session Metadata: Persistent throughout quiz  \n\n---\n\n### **3.4 Feedback & Results Module**\n\n#### **3.4.1 Immediate Feedback**\n\n**Visual Indicators:**\n\n- ✅ Green checkmark for correct  \n- ❌ Red X for incorrect  \n- Color-coded result text  \n\n**Audio Feedback:**\n\n- Correct answer sound effect  \n- Wrong answer sound effect  \n- Volume set to 13% of max  \n- Preloaded for low latency  \n\n**Toast Notifications:**\n\n- \"Correct!\" message  \n- \"Wrong!\" message  \n- \"Time's up!\" for timeouts  \n- Color-coded (green/red)  \n\n---\n\n#### **3.4.2 Explanation Display**\n\n- Shows correct answer explanation  \n- Displayed immediately after submission  \n- Remains visible until next question  \n\n---\n\n#### **3.4.3 Navigation Controls**\n\n- \"Next Question\" button:  \n  - Loads subsequent question  \n  - Changes to \"Finish Quiz\" on last question  \n- Transition: Smooth loading state between questions  \n\n---\n\n### **3.5 Quiz Summary Module**\n\n#### **3.5.1 End-of-Session Summary**\n\n**Displays:**\n\n- Total questions completed (15)  \n- Final score (total points)  \n- Correct answer count  \n- Accuracy percentage  \n\n**Formatted Display:**\n\n- Large, centered presentation  \n- Bold emphasis on key metrics  \n- Congratulatory header  \n\n---\n\n#### **3.5.2 Session Reset**\n\n- \"Restart Quiz\" button:  \n  - Returns to setup screen  \n  - Clears all session data  \n  - Resets score and progress  \n  - Clears used question pool  \n\n---\n\n### **3.6 UI/UX Components**\n\n#### **3.6.1 Loading States**\n\n- Animation: Spinning loader  \n- Message: \"Getting a question…\"  \n- Duration: 200–900ms depending on source  \n\n---\n\n#### **3.6.2 Error Handling**\n\n**Error Display:**\n\n- Error message shown  \n- \"Try Again\" button  \n- Returns to setup on retry  \n\n**Error Scenarios:**\n\n- Question fetch failure  \n- Empty question bank  \n- Network issues  \n\n---\n\n#### **3.6.3 Responsive Design**\n\n**Mobile-optimized:**\n\n- Flexible padding (px-4 sm:px-8)  \n- Responsive layout  \n- Touch-friendly controls  \n\n**Card-based UI:**\n\n- Rounded corners  \n- Shadow effects  \n- White background  \n- Consistent spacing  \n\n---\n\n#### **3.6.4 Animations**\n\n**CSS Transitions:**\n\n- Scale-in on setup  \n- Fade-in effects  \n- Hover effects on buttons  \n- Pulse animation on loading  \n\n**Smooth Transitions:**\n\n- State changes  \n- Question transitions  \n\n---\n\n### **3.7 Ads Integration Module (Referenced)**\n\n**Component:**\n\n- AdsSidebar  \n\n**Functionality:**\n\n- Displays contextual ads  \n- Topic-aware ad selection  \n- Updates on topic change  \n\n---\n\n## **4. Technical Features**\n\n### **4.1 State Management**\n\n- React hooks-based state  \n- Session-level persistence  \n- No backend authentication  \n- Local storage not utilized  \n\n### **4.2 Quiz States**\n\n- Setup  \n- Loading  \n- Question  \n- Result  \n- Summary  \n- Error  \n\n### **4.3 Data Structures**\n\n- Question bank per topic  \n- Question object: question, options, correct answer, explanation  \n- Session statistics tracking  \n\n### **4.4 Audio System**\n\n- Sound effect preloading  \n- Error-tolerant playback  \n- Browser compatibility handling  \n\n---\n\n## **5. User Flow**\n\n1. Entry: User lands on quiz setup  \n2. Configuration: Select topic and difficulty  \n3. Quiz Start: First question loads with timer  \n4. Question Loop:  \n   - View question and options  \n   - Select answer or wait for timeout  \n   - Submit answer  \n   - View result and explanation  \n   - Click next or skip to new question  \n5. Completion: After 15 questions, see summary  \n6. Exit: Restart quiz or close application  \n\n---\n\n## **6. Constraints & Limitations**\n\n- Maximum 15 questions per session  \n- 30-second timer per question (non-configurable)  \n- 3 answer options only (A, B, C)  \n- No user accounts or progress persistence  \n- No question bookmarking or review  \n- No pause functionality  \n- LLM integration for custom topics is placeholder  \n\n---\n\n## **7. Non-Functional Requirements**\n\n**Performance:**\n\n- Question load time: <1 second  \n- Audio playback: Immediate  \n- UI transitions: Smooth (300ms)  \n\n**Accessibility:**\n\n- Color-coded feedback  \n- Audio + visual cues  \n- Keyboard navigation support (form inputs)  \n\n**Browser Support:**\n\n- Modern browsers with ES6+ support  \n- Audio API support required  \n\n`